</para>
<para>The sensor driver controller device structure will be retrieved by calling macro DEVICE_DT_GET and function checks if the device is ready for usage with call of function device_is_ready. The return value ready of this function will be assigned to flag device_good. In case of an error a debug message at error level will be printed. </para>
