        <briefdescription>
<para>Function to sample temperature and humidity data from sensor. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para><hruler/>
</para>
<para>With call of function sensor_sample_fetch provided by the zephyr API sample temperature and humidity data will be fetched from the sensor and stored it in an internal driver buffer. Afterwards the timestamp for this sample will be stored in private member variable sample_ts. </para>
